    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! You seriously have to see this beauty in person\u2014it honestly looks like it just rolled off the showroom floor. I've babied this car since day one, and it\u2019s in absolutely flawless shape inside and out. No scratches, no spills, just pure perfection. It\u2019s been my pride and joy, but it's ready for its next adventure with someone who will love it just as much as I have. Drop me a message if you want to come by, grab a coffee, and take it for a spin!",
