    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Offered here is a truly exceptional vehicle that presents in showroom condition. The exterior paint retains a deep, mirror-like luster, completely free of the swirl marks, stone chips, or imperfections typically found on pre-owned cars. Every body panel is laser-straight with perfect factory gaps. Inside, the cabin is a sanctuary; the premium leather upholstery remains supple and matte, showing absolutely no bolster wear or creasing, and it still retains that distinct 'new car' fragrance. All technological features, from the high-fidelity sound system to the driver-assist suite, operate with precision. Mechanically, this car has been pampered, stored in a climate-controlled garage, and maintained strictly according to the manufacturer\u2019s schedule with a documented service history. The engine bay is immaculate, and the original alloy wheels are devoid of any curb rash. This is a rare opportunity for a discerning buyer to acquire a vehicle that is indistinguishable from new.",
      "price": 48500.0,
