      "description": "Available is an investment-grade E46 M3, showcasing the pinnacle of the S54 naturally aspirated 3.2L inline-six. This specimen features a surgically precise 6-speed Getrag manual gearbox and a fully documented subframe reinforcement, addressing the chassis's primary structural vulnerability. The high-pressure Vanos system has been overhauled with Beisan components, and the rod bearings were proactively replaced to ensure long-term reciprocating assembly integrity. Performance is anchored by a variable M differential lock and factory-spec dampers that maintain original compression and rebound characteristics. With zero oxidation on the undercarriage and a factory-fresh power band characterized by its 8,000 RPM redline and individual throttle body response, this is a turnkey collector-grade vehicle for the discerning purist.",
